[
  {
    "text": " ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=2"
  },
  {
    "text": "Hi! ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=9"
  },
  {
    "text": "Welcome to WWDC. My name's Yongjun. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=10"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm an engineer from App Clips team. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=13"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm joined today by my colleague, Luming, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=15"
  },
  {
    "text": "to talk about what's new in App Clips. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=17"
  },
  {
    "text": "An App Clip is a small part of an app that can be launched ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=20"
  },
  {
    "text": "at the moment when it's needed. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=24"
  },
  {
    "text": "It provides fast and focused experience on a specific task. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=26"
  },
  {
    "text": "User can easily upgrade to your app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=30"
  },
  {
    "text": "after they complete the task. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=33"
  },
  {
    "text": "Since it's launched, we have seen many great App Clips ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=35"
  },
  {
    "text": "from developers all over the world. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=38"
  },
  {
    "text": "They are well designed, easily discoverable, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=41"
  },
  {
    "text": "with great ways to engage users. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=43"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let me share some examples with you. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=45"
  },
  {
    "text": "Firi Games has an App Clip ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=48"
  },
  {
    "text": "for their popular Phoenix 2 game. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=50"
  },
  {
    "text": "I can go to their web site in Safari, tap the banner. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=52"
  },
  {
    "text": "It will show the App Clip Card for this game. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=56"
  },
  {
    "text": "From there, I can launch the game. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=59"
  },
  {
    "text": "In a couple seconds, the game's ready to play. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=62"
  },
  {
    "text": "After I play the first level, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=67"
  },
  {
    "text": "I can download the full game right from the App Clip. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=69"
  },
  {
    "text": "TikTok has an App Clip ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=73"
  },
  {
    "text": "to make sharing video really fun and easy. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=75"
  },
  {
    "text": "When I receive a video from my friend, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=78"
  },
  {
    "text": "iMessage will show the TikTok App Clip preview. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=80"
  },
  {
    "text": "Tap of the preview shows the card. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=85"
  },
  {
    "text": "There I can open TikTok App Clip. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=87"
  },
  {
    "text": "I can enjoy the video right away. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=90"
  },
  {
    "text": "Panera bread is a U.S.-based food service ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=93"
  },
  {
    "text": "with thousands of stores. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=96"
  },
  {
    "text": "If I look up one of the stores in Maps, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=98"
  },
  {
    "text": "the place card will show \"order food\" action button. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=101"
  },
  {
    "text": "I can open their App Clip right from there. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=104"
  },
  {
    "text": "Within seconds, the App Clip launches ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=107"
  },
  {
    "text": "and shows the menu for this particular store. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=109"
  },
  {
    "text": "I can make order and pay with Apple Pay. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=113"
  },
  {
    "text": "In iOS 15, if I search a business in Spotlight, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=116"
  },
  {
    "text": "like Panera, the App Clip will show up in search results, too. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=119"
  },
  {
    "text": "With on-device intelligence, if I'm nearby Panera store, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=124"
  },
  {
    "text": "my phone can suggest the App Clip ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=128"
  },
  {
    "text": "to me in Siri suggestion widget. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=130"
  },
  {
    "text": "Tap the suggestion, I can open it and order food right away. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=133"
  },
  {
    "text": "Honk created an App Clip ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=138"
  },
  {
    "text": "for touchless payment for parking. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=140"
  },
  {
    "text": "All I need to do is scan their QR code ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=142"
  },
  {
    "text": "attached at the parking lot. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=145"
  },
  {
    "text": "With one tap, I can open the App Clip ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=147"
  },
  {
    "text": "and pay with Apple Pay. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=149"
  },
  {
    "text": "Primer AR Home Design has an App Clip for you to try ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=152"
  },
  {
    "text": "paint, tile, and wallpaper in an AR environment. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=155"
  },
  {
    "text": "I can scan or tap the App Clip code ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=159"
  },
  {
    "text": "on a tile to open the App Clip. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=162"
  },
  {
    "text": "There, I can experience how this beautiful tile ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=165"
  },
  {
    "text": "would look like in my living room. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=168"
  },
  {
    "text": "These are some great example App Clips. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=171"
  },
  {
    "text": "There are many, many more. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=173"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can discovered them in Safari, Messages, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=175"
  },
  {
    "text": "or in the real world by a QR code, NFC tag, or App Clip code. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=178"
  },
  {
    "text": "I encourage you to try them out and see what App Clips can do. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=183"
  },
  {
    "text": "In this session, we will cover three topics. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=188"
  },
  {
    "text": "First, App Clip Card in Safari and SafariViewController. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=191"
  },
  {
    "text": "Then, we will talk about testing App Clip with local experiences. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=196"
  },
  {
    "text": "Last, we will cover App Clip code.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=201"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's look at a new way to explore App Clips. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=207"
  },
  {
    "text": "Your website can use apple-itunes-app meta tag ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=211"
  },
  {
    "text": "to display the smart app banner ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=214"
  },
  {
    "text": "in Safari or Safari View Controller. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=216"
  },
  {
    "text": "In iOS 15, you can configure the meta tag to show ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=219"
  },
  {
    "text": "a full-sized App Clip Card, right in the middle of web page. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=223"
  },
  {
    "text": "User can open your App Clip from there. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=227"
  },
  {
    "text": "If they choose \"View in Safari,\" Safari will remember the choice ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=231"
  },
  {
    "text": "and not show the card next time the page is loaded again. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=234"
  },
  {
    "text": "And it will fall back to the original banner. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=237"
  },
  {
    "text": "To opt-in card mode, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=241"
  },
  {
    "text": "you just need to add \"app-clip-display\" key ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=243"
  },
  {
    "text": "to the meta tag and set it to \"card.\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=246"
  },
  {
    "text": "The card mode works great ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=250"
  },
  {
    "text": "if you like to promote your App Clip in the web page. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=253"
  },
  {
    "text": "For apps using SafariViewController ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=256"
  },
  {
    "text": "to render web content, like Twitter, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=258"
  },
  {
    "text": "it can show the card as a part of the app's UI. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=260"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, user can launch the App Clip ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=264"
  },
  {
    "text": "directly from the app.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=266"
  },
  {
    "text": "This is the App Clip Card in Safari ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=273"
  },
  {
    "text": "and SafariViewController. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=275"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's talk about test with local experiences. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=277"
  },
  {
    "text": "For users, their App Clip experience ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=282"
  },
  {
    "text": "starts with the App Clip Card. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=284"
  },
  {
    "text": "The card shows your App Clip's title, subtitle, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=288"
  },
  {
    "text": "what action can take, and a header image ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=291"
  },
  {
    "text": "to show your brand and style. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=294"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can create an App Clip Card in App Store Connect. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=296"
  },
  {
    "text": "Follow the step-by-step guide to configure all the elements. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=300"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can also specify locations associated with your App Clip. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=303"
  },
  {
    "text": "This could make the App Clip show up in Maps place card, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=307"
  },
  {
    "text": "Siri suggestion widget, or Spotlight search. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=311"
  },
  {
    "text": "To know about how to customize App Clip Card, please refer ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=316"
  },
  {
    "text": "to WWDC20 sessions, \"What's new in App Store Connect\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=320"
  },
  {
    "text": "and \"Configure and link your App Clips.\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=324"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, when you develop your App Clip, you might ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=326"
  },
  {
    "text": "not have registered any App Clip experiences yet. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=329"
  },
  {
    "text": "Sometimes, you do want to test the end-to-end flow ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=333"
  },
  {
    "text": "and role-play the whole experience. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=336"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can do that with local experiences. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=338"
  },
  {
    "text": "A local experience is an experience you enter ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=341"
  },
  {
    "text": "in your own testing device. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=344"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can launch it with most ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=346"
  },
  {
    "text": "of regular App Clip invocation methods. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=347"
  },
  {
    "text": "To create a local experience, go to Developer Settings ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=351"
  },
  {
    "text": "and select Local Experiences. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=354"
  },
  {
    "text": "Specify your App Clip's name, title, URL prefix, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=357"
  },
  {
    "text": "bundleID, and select an image ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=361"
  },
  {
    "text": "in your photo library as the header image. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=363"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can then scan a QR code or NFC tag ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=366"
  },
  {
    "text": "to launch the experience. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=370"
  },
  {
    "text": "Local experiences support QR, NFC, App Clip Code, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=372"
  },
  {
    "text": "Safari, and Messages. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=376"
  },
  {
    "text": "They don't show up in Maps, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=378"
  },
  {
    "text": "location suggestions, and Spotlight search. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=380"
  },
  {
    "text": "These require registered experiences. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=383"
  },
  {
    "text": "Also, you can only specify local experiences ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=386"
  },
  {
    "text": "for Xcode-installed App Clips or App Clips in Beta testing. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=389"
  },
  {
    "text": "This is how you can test with local experiences. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=393"
  },
  {
    "text": "With that, I would like to hand over ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=396"
  },
  {
    "text": "to Luming to show you a demo. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=398"
  },
  {
    "text": "Thanks, Yongjun! ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=401"
  },
  {
    "text": "As Yongjun mentioned in the talk, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=403"
  },
  {
    "text": "you can now configure the meta tag ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=405"
  },
  {
    "text": "to show a full-sized App Clip Card right in the middle ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=407"
  },
  {
    "text": "of the web page in both Safari and SafariViewController.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=411"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm in the FoodGrid app, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=418"
  },
  {
    "text": "a third-party app my friend has built, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=420"
  },
  {
    "text": "which helps you discover nearby restaurants ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=422"
  },
  {
    "text": "and beverage shops. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=424"
  },
  {
    "text": "As you can see, my smoothie stand, Fruta, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=426"
  },
  {
    "text": "is featured in this FoodGrid app. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=428"
  },
  {
    "text": "Tapping on my smoothie stand, Fruta, in my friend's app opens ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=431"
  },
  {
    "text": "a SafariViewController showing my smoothie stand website. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=434"
  },
  {
    "text": "Because my smoothie stand website has already adopted ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=438"
  },
  {
    "text": "Smart App Banner meta tag for iOS 14 and iPadOS 14, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=441"
  },
  {
    "text": "my customers can open the Fruta App Clip ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=446"
  },
  {
    "text": "from the Smart App Banner, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=448"
  },
  {
    "text": "but opening the App Clip this way requires the customer ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=450"
  },
  {
    "text": "discovering the banner, tapping open, then confirming it ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=453"
  },
  {
    "text": "in the App Clip Card, which is a multi step process. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=457"
  },
  {
    "text": "So, adopting the new full-sized App Clip Card for iOS 15 ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=460"
  },
  {
    "text": "and iPadOS 15 is a great way to promote and elevate discovery ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=465"
  },
  {
    "text": "of our Fruta smoothie stand App Clip ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=470"
  },
  {
    "text": "within the web page or within third-party apps ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=472"
  },
  {
    "text": "that embed our website through SafariViewController. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=476"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's see how to do just that. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=479"
  },
  {
    "text": "Here, I am on the Fruta web server that hosts our website. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=481"
  },
  {
    "text": "Within the apple-itunes-app meta tag, I just need ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=486"
  },
  {
    "text": "to add \"app-clip-display,\" and set its value to \"card.\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=490"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, if I tap to open the restaurant website again ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=495"
  },
  {
    "text": "in the FoodGrid app, you will notice ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=499"
  },
  {
    "text": "the App Clip Card shows up immediately ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=501"
  },
  {
    "text": "within the web page as a part of the FoodGrid app's UI. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=503"
  },
  {
    "text": "The user can then launch the Fruta App Clip ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=507"
  },
  {
    "text": "directly from this third-party app. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=509"
  },
  {
    "text": "Back to you, Yongjun. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=513"
  },
  {
    "text": "Thank you, Luming. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=514"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, I know how to launch my App Clip ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=516"
  },
  {
    "text": "from the app with the help of SFSafariViewController. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=518"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, let's talk about App Clip code. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=521"
  },
  {
    "text": "App Clip code is a new, Apple-designed visual code. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=525"
  },
  {
    "text": "It is the best way to discover App Clip experiences ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=528"
  },
  {
    "text": "in the real world. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=531"
  },
  {
    "text": "It is available from iOS 14.3. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=533"
  },
  {
    "text": "So, there are almost 1 billion devices ready ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=537"
  },
  {
    "text": "for your App Clip code. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=539"
  },
  {
    "text": "An App Clip code always leads to an App Clip. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=541"
  },
  {
    "text": "When the user sees such a code, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=545"
  },
  {
    "text": "they know there's an App Clip to explore. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=547"
  },
  {
    "text": "Each code encodes a unique URL for specific experience. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=551"
  },
  {
    "text": "iOS decodes the URL before sending to the App Clip. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=555"
  },
  {
    "text": "This means your App Clip doesn't need ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=559"
  },
  {
    "text": "to do anything special to handle these codes. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=561"
  },
  {
    "text": "Your existing URL handling will just work. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=564"
  },
  {
    "text": "There are two types of App Clip code: ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=568"
  },
  {
    "text": "NFC integrated or Scan only. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=571"
  },
  {
    "text": "User can interact with NFC-integrated code ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=574"
  },
  {
    "text": "by tap it or scanning it with the camera. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=577"
  },
  {
    "text": "Use this type when customer can easily access the code. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=579"
  },
  {
    "text": "For example, on a vending machine, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=583"
  },
  {
    "text": "or on a restaurant table, or on storefront window. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=585"
  },
  {
    "text": "Use scan only if the code may be placed out of reach ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=589"
  },
  {
    "text": "for the customer, or when NFC is not appropriate. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=593"
  },
  {
    "text": "For example, when it is displayed digitally ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=597"
  },
  {
    "text": "in a marketing email. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=600"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can customize the style of App Clip code ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=604"
  },
  {
    "text": "to fit specific use cases. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=607"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can pick you own foreground or background color. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=609"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can also hide the App Clip logo. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=613"
  },
  {
    "text": "We suggest to show the logo when there is enough space. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=615"
  },
  {
    "text": "This gives new customer a clear message ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=619"
  },
  {
    "text": "that it is for App Clips. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=622"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you have an ARKit App Clip, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=624"
  },
  {
    "text": "you can use App Clip code as an anchor, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=627"
  },
  {
    "text": "tracking its position in the physical world. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=630"
  },
  {
    "text": "This could bring amazing experiences. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=632"
  },
  {
    "text": "For example, a user can scan an App Clip code ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=635"
  },
  {
    "text": "on a package, exploring what is inside, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=637"
  },
  {
    "text": "like this guitar, without opening the package. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=640"
  },
  {
    "text": "To know more about App Clip code and ARKit, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=644"
  },
  {
    "text": "please check out WWDC21 session, \"Explore ARKit 5.\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=647"
  },
  {
    "text": "There are two ways to create an App Clip code. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=653"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can use the App Clip Code Generator tool, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=656"
  },
  {
    "text": "available from developer.apple.com, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=658"
  },
  {
    "text": "or you can download the code directly from App Store Connect. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=661"
  },
  {
    "text": "We recommend to use the command-line tool ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=666"
  },
  {
    "text": "when you're testing or developing an App Clip, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=669"
  },
  {
    "text": "or you need to automate code generation. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=671"
  },
  {
    "text": "Use App Store Connect to create codes for registered URLs. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=675"
  },
  {
    "text": "For the best scanning experience, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=680"
  },
  {
    "text": "here are some guidelines to keep in mind. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=682"
  },
  {
    "text": "First, keep the code on a flat surface. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=684"
  },
  {
    "text": "The code should be placed at upright position. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=688"
  },
  {
    "text": "Make sure you don't rotate the code or the central logo. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=691"
  },
  {
    "text": "Small codes are harder for customers to see and scan, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=696"
  },
  {
    "text": "so make sure your code is large enough, at least 1 inch wide.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=700"
  },
  {
    "text": "Ensure good visibility. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=706"
  },
  {
    "text": "Make sure your code is not blocked, damaged, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=708"
  },
  {
    "text": "or placed too close to other codes. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=711"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can add a text next to the code to inform people ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=716"
  },
  {
    "text": "how they can use it to launch your App Clip. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=719"
  },
  {
    "text": "Make sure the message is concise and with a clear call to action. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=722"
  },
  {
    "text": "For more information, please check ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=727"
  },
  {
    "text": "the Human Interface Guidelines and This is App Clip Code. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=729"
  },
  {
    "text": "I would like to hand over to Luming, again, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=734"
  },
  {
    "text": "to show you how to quickly generate App Clip Codes. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=737"
  },
  {
    "text": "Thanks, Yongjun! ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=740"
  },
  {
    "text": "As Yongjun mentioned, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=743"
  },
  {
    "text": "the easiest way to generate an App Clip Code is ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=744"
  },
  {
    "text": "to download it from App Store Connect. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=747"
  },
  {
    "text": "For cases where you need more customization, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=750"
  },
  {
    "text": "or need to script App Clip Code generation in bulk, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=753"
  },
  {
    "text": "generating them locally using the App Clip Code Generator ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=757"
  },
  {
    "text": "command-line tool is a great option. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=761"
  },
  {
    "text": "I've already downloaded and installed ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=764"
  },
  {
    "text": "App Clip Code Generator from the Apple Developer website ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=766"
  },
  {
    "text": "onto my Mac, so I can open Terminal ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=769"
  },
  {
    "text": "and interact with the tool. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=772"
  },
  {
    "text": "It's really easy to use. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=773"
  },
  {
    "text": "As Yongjun mentioned, there are a variety ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=775"
  },
  {
    "text": "of templates available to choose. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=778"
  },
  {
    "text": "And I can enter \"App Clip Code Generator templates\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=780"
  },
  {
    "text": "to view a list of all available templates. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=784"
  },
  {
    "text": "But how do these templates look, exactly? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=788"
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, you can find a preview of all ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=791"
  },
  {
    "text": "of these template at the following location: ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=793"
  },
  {
    "text": "/Library/Developer/AppClipCode Generator/SampleTemplates. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=796"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's look at these using Quick Look.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=802"
  },
  {
    "text": "Number 4 looks really great, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=809"
  },
  {
    "text": "so I'm going to generate an App Clip Code ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=812"
  },
  {
    "text": "using this template for our Fruta App Clip. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=814"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll enter \"AppClipCodeGenerator generate.\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=818"
  },
  {
    "text": "We'll generate an NFC App Clip Code ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=822"
  },
  {
    "text": "since I'll place an NFC tag ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=825"
  },
  {
    "text": "behind the printed App Clip Code. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=827"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll pass in a URL that I have registered ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=831"
  },
  {
    "text": "as an advanced App Clip experience ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=834"
  },
  {
    "text": "on App Store Connect, which is fruta.example. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=836"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll choose template 4, which we figure looks great ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=840"
  },
  {
    "text": "from the Quick Look preview in Finder. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=844"
  },
  {
    "text": "Finally, I'll pass in ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=848"
  },
  {
    "text": "the desired output SVG file name fruta.svg.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=850"
  },
  {
    "text": "SVG graphics are vector based, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=856"
  },
  {
    "text": "so they scale beautifully when you print them ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=858"
  },
  {
    "text": "from a piece of U.S.-letter-sized paper, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=861"
  },
  {
    "text": "all the way to a 24-by-36 poster. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=863"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's open a generated SVG in Safari to preview it.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=867"
  },
  {
    "text": "I have already printed this App Clip Code ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=875"
  },
  {
    "text": "on a poster, so let's try scanning it ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=878"
  },
  {
    "text": "from the Code Scanner module in Control Center.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=880"
  },
  {
    "text": "And here we are. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=893"
  },
  {
    "text": "We are now in the Fruta App Clip. ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=894"
  },
  {
    "text": "And that is a quick demonstration ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=897"
  },
  {
    "text": "of how to generate App Clip Code using ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2021/10012/?time=900"
  },
  {
